description.narrative: UNICEF Lao PDR has made strong progress in strengthening its partnerships including with Government counterparts, donors, media, the UN family and with youth organizations. The office also made strategic use of public advocacy and events such as the Lao Generation 2030 Initiative, media engagement, community mobilization and youth engagement to raise awareness and engagement in child rights issues. Thanks to these important partnerships, children's and women's rights have been promoted and specific commitments to improve children's lives have been signed, marking an important milestone in the country, coinciding with CRC30. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2019
